snippet.title: Wargroove 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wargroove is back! A sequel to the award-winning strategy game is in development for PC and Nintendo Switch. Wishlist now: https://bit.ly/Wargroove2_Steam

Trouble stirs on the shores of Aurania. An ambitious new faction has unearthed forbidden relics capable of catastrophic consequences. But how far will they go to achieve glory? Take to the battlefield, sea, and sky with a cast of new Commanders, using your wits to wage turn-based war!

Developed by Robotality & Chucklefish. Published by Chucklefish.

https://wargroove.com/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/Wargroove
Follow Wargroove on Twitter: https://twitter.com/WargrooveGame
